folder: Vanderbilt Ave. & Atlantic Ave., Brooklyn, NY
text:
Vanderbilt Ave., east side, from and including Atlantic Ave., to, but not including Fulton Street. A view of two 3-story frame houses, alongside of an old public auditorium. In the background, may be seen the steeple of St. Luke's Protestant Episcopal Church.

November 26, 1927.

P. L. Sperr.
